{"tid":1425278,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有感而發","createTime":"2019-08-06T17:37:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:37:25.000Z","uid":286533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"eb82234a5a0ceff7958ffa6c03c07fb1e0a1e675","tid":1425278,"uid":286533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T17:37:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/PeopleOfHK/videos/340852300198567?s=100001553854665&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPeopleOfHK%2Fvideos%2F340852300198567%3Fs%3D100001553854665%26v%3De%26sfns%3Dxmo&d=%2FAyHQi%2FQiMXiPJLA4RPCZobsTeectjBlsojPGUwt5kI%3D&h=3dce8434\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/PeopleOfHK/videos/340852300198567?s=100001553854665&amp;v=e&amp;sfns=xmo</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aNOecXg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaNOecXg.png&h=349aa8c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我真係睇到好嬲<br />\n經剪接嘅野真係唔好信<br />\n我知同佢哋講做鍵盤戰士係無用<br />\n所以想係呢到釋放下自己情緒<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依佢哋咁講<br />\n駛車衝入人群係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">謀殺</span><br />\n持刀衝向示威者揮刀係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">謀殺</span><br />\n高空擲物<span style=\"font-size: large;\">重要係玻璃</span>更係<span style=\"font-size: large;\">謀殺</span><br />\n<br />\n咁警察向人群扔催淚彈同射海綿彈係咪知法犯法？<br />\n<br />\n警方用過激嘅武力去<span style=\"color: navy;\">驅散人群</span> 就得<br />\n我哋用適當嘅武力去保護自己就唔得？？？<br />\n<br />\n成班死廢老無諗過點解會搞成咁嘅局面<br />\n點解我哋付出咗2個幾月去改變呢個香港佢哋會當我哋係垃圾咁睇<br />\n點解要怪我哋表達嘅方法而唔係怪政府嘅<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">無能</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n我好興幸自己生存係呢個世代，可以親身經歷而家所發生嘅一切。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">香港人加油</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span>"}]}